        <APP>\vcd <LEM>bandhur{ }nā°</LEM> \mssALL\msCa\msNa\Ed; bandhu nā° \msCb\msNb\msNc</APP>
        <APP>\vd <LEM>japa°</LEM> \mssALL\msCa\msCb\msNa\msNc\ \unmetr; japassamaḥ \msNb, japaḥsamaḥ \Ed</APP>
        <TR>There is no relative comparable to knowledge. There is no worship comparable to recitation.</TR>
